  ],
  "bodyHtml": "<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">As a seller on Back Market, you have to provide invoices to your customers after their purchases. Of course, those invoices must contain specific information to be compliant with the law. In this regard, we would like to provide you with all the necessary elements to make sure you know how to establish correctly an invoice.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>What should appear an all invoices, no matters if you&#39;re in marginal VAT or not:</strong></span></h2>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> </div>\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Seller Information</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Registration Number</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Place of establishment</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">VAT registration Number</span></li></ul>\n</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Customer Information</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Name</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Address</span></li></ul>\n</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Bill Information</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Number</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Date</span></li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> </div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>What should appear on the invoice if you&#39;re in marginal VAT:</strong></span></h2>\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Seller&#39;s legal notices</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Corporate name</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Head office or legal domicile</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Registration/incorporation number</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">VAT number</span></li></ul>\n</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Client&#39;s legal notices (individual consumer)</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Name &amp; last name</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Address</span></li></ul>\n</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Invoicing legal notices</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Date</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Invoice Number</span></li></ul>\n</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Legal notice regarding the service provision</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Operation date if different from the one on the invoice</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Quantity and precise of the goods delivered</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Price excluding taxes</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Discount if appropriate</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Delivery fees</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">State: VAT Non-applicable special scheme, second hand goods)</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Total amount including VAT</span></li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>What should appear on the invoice if you&#39;re not in m</strong><strong>arginal VAT:</strong></span></h2>\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Seller&#39;s legal notices</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Corporate name</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Head office or legal domicile</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Registration/incorporation number</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">VAT number</span></li></ul>\n</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Client&#39;s legal notices (individual consumer)</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Name &amp; last name</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Address</span></li></ul>\n</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Invoicing legal notices</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Date</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Invoice Number</span></li></ul>\n</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Legal notice regarding the service provision</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Operation date if different from the one on the invoice</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Quantity and precise of the goods delivered</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Price excluding taxes</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Discount if appropriate</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Delivery fees</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">VAT rate of country of arrival</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">VAT amount of country of arrival</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Total amount including VAT</span></li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>What language do I need to provide the receipt in?</strong></span></h2>\n<p><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">If your customer asks for a receipt in the language of the market they purchased in, you must provide it. (You can find this in article 6.1 of the seller T&amp;Cs: The seller must communicate with any buyer in the language of the country where the buyer accessed the marketplace).</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>How long am I required to provide the receipt for?</strong></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Your customer can also ask for the receipt up to 2 years after the purchase in France and Spain, for 6 years in the UK, and 3 years in Germany. Keep in mind that after you’re no longer legally required to provide the customer receipt, you may be asked for it for up to 10 years by authorities for accounting purposes.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Please note that in some countries, e-invoicing or e-reporting obligations may apply. It is the seller’s responsibility to ensure compliance with local regulations.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><a href=\"https://backmarket.my.site.com/ssc/s/article/How-do-you-generate-an-invoice-for-a-client\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #3498db;\">Check out this article for more information on how to upload a receipt for your customer</span></a></strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">➡️  If you&#39;re facing issues in establishing your invoices or if you still have some questions, please feel free to <strong>contact</strong> the Seller Support via the <b><a href=\"https://backmarket.my.site.com/ssc/s/submit-new-request\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #3498db;\">forms</span></a> </b>in the <strong>SSC</strong>.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><em>Back Market in no way guarantees the accuracy or completeness of the information contained in this article and disclaims all liability in this respect.</em></span></p>"
